                        <h3 class="my-3">Use Disposal of Unwanted Medicines</h3>
                        <p>
                            According to the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention report every year more than 60, 000 children were ended up with emergency hospital admission from taking unwanted medicines when families not at home or looking. In addition, leftover prescriptions medicines is an easy sources for someone who thinking for abusing medicines. The best mechanisms to dispose of an unwanted, old, unused, and expired medicine is to drop off or request collecting organization for pick up the medicine at medicine collect site. The main objective of this project to simplify for elderly, people with disabilities, someone do not get transportation access, and anyone interested to request medicine disposal from home.

                            In St. Louis city, there are limited medicines disposal locations. Even if the location exist, it requires someone to take a medicine at specific drop of locations. The creation of “Disposal of Unwanted Medicines” website will make easy for everyone want to request services.
                        </p>
                       


